A simple **Java Swing** desktop application that simulates a banking management system.  
It allows users to **create accounts, log in, deposit, withdraw, transfer funds**, and check their account status â€” all with a clean and user-friendly GUI.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- **Create Account** â€“ Register with your name, date of birth, phone number, and password.
- **Login / Logout** â€“ Secure login system with password authentication.
- **Deposit Money** â€“ Add funds to your account.
- **Withdraw Money** â€“ Withdraw cash if sufficient balance is available.
- **Transfer Money** â€“ Send money to another account using their phone number.
- **Account Status** â€“ View your personal details and current balance when logged in.
- **Show All Accounts** â€“ View the list of all accounts (name & account number only).
- **Persistent Storage** â€“ Data is saved using Java serialization (`accounts.ser`).

